msgid: Configure for how long the infobar will remain visible after activation.

msgid: Configure for how many minutes finished events should remain visible in the EPG. Useful when you need information about an event which has just finished, or has been delayed.
openpli: Nastavitev trajanja vidnosti končanih dogodkov v EPG sistemu. To je uporabno takrat, ko zamudite neko oddajo ali film, a bi za nazaj vseeno želeli izvedeti določene informacije o tem dogodku (npr. angleško ime filma).

msgid: Configure how many channels are shown in the selection list.
Configure how recording filenames are constructed.

msgid: Configure how the fan should operate
Configure if and how crypto icons will be shown in the channel selection list.

msgid: Configure if and how long the latest service in Picture in Picture mode will be remembered.
openpli: Določitev vklopa nastavitve in kako dolgo naj si sprejemnik zapomni zadnji gledani kanal v načinu \"Slika v sliki\".

msgid: Configure if and how service type icons will be shown in the channel selection list.
openpli: Določitev morebitnega prikaza ter načina prikaza ikon, ki prikazujejo vrsto kanala (kabel, antena, satelit) v seznamu kanalov.

msgid: Configure if and how the record indicator will be shown in the channel selection list.
openpli: Določitev morebitnega prikaza indikatorja snemanja v seznamu kanalov.

msgid: Configure if and how wide columns will be shown in the channel selection list.
openpli: Določitev morebitnega prikaza in širine stolpcev v seznamu kanalov.

msgid: Configure if behind the subtitles a background is shown.
Configure if service picons will be shown in display (when supported by the skin).
Configure if service picons will be shown in the channel selection list.
openpli: Določitev prikaza majhnih slik kanalov (t.i. piconsi) v seznamu kanalov.

msgid: Configure if the HDMI EDID checking should be bypassed as this might solve issue with some TVs.
Configure if the subtitle should switch between normal, italic, bold and bolditalic
openpli: Določitev možnosti preklapljanja podnapisov med navadnimi, poševnimi, odebeljenimi in poševnimi/odebeljenimi.

msgid: Configure on which devices the background delete option should be used.
openpli: Nastavitev omogoča, da določite, na katerih napravah naj bo uporabljena možnost \"izbrisa v ozadju\".

msgid: Configure the DiSEqC mode for this LNB.
openpli: Nastavitev DiSEqC načina za ta LNB.

msgid: Configure the aspect ratio of the screen.
Configure the behavior of the 'pause and ok' key when movie playback is already paused.
openpli: Določitev obnašanja tipk \"premor\" in  \"OK\", ko je posnetek že pavziran.

msgid: Configure the behavior when movie playback is manually stopped.
openpli: Nastavitev obnašanja pri ročno ustavljeni video datoteki.

msgid: Configure the behavior when movie playback is started.
openpli: Nastavitev obnašanja, ko se prične predvajanje posnetka.

msgid: Configure the behavior when reaching the end of a movie, during movie playback.
openpli: Določitev obnašanja sprejemnika, ko se video posnetek približuje koncu.

msgid: Configure the border width of the subtitles. The dark border makes the subtitles easier to read on a light background.
openpli: Določitev širine obrobe pisave pri podnapisih. Temnejša obroba omogoči lažje branje podnapisov na svetlejši podlagi.

msgid: Configure the brightness level of the front panel display during standby.
openpli: Določitev ravni svetlosti sprednjega zaslona sprejemnika, ko se le-ta nahaja v stanju pripravljenosti.

msgid: Configure the brightness level of the front panel display.
openpli: Določitev ravni svetlosti sprednjega zaslona sprejemnika.

msgid: Configure the color of the external subtitles, alternative (normal in white, italic in yellow, bold in cyan, underscore in green), white or yellow.
openpli: Določitev barve zunanjih podnapisov. Izbirate lahko med mešano (normalni podnapisi v beli, poševni v rumeni, odebeljeni v modri ter podčrtani v zeleni barvi), belo in rumeno barvo.

msgid: Configure the color of the teletext subtitles.
Configure the contrast level of the front panel display.

Configure the cursor behaviour in the channel selection list. When opening the channel selection list you can keep on the current service or already select up/down and you are able to revert the B+/B- buttons.
openpli: Določitev vedenja kazalca v seznamu kanalov. Izberete lahko, da je ob odprtju seznama kanalov kazalec na kanalu, ki ga trenutno gledate, da se ob odprtju seznama kazalec premakne v smer pritisnjene tipke (gor/dol), lahko pa spreminjate tudi smer premikanja pri pritisku tipk B+/-.

msgid: Configure the duration in hours the receiver should go to standby when the receiver is not controlled.
openpli: Določitev trajanja v urah, ko gre sprejemnik v stanje pripravljenosti, če sprejemnik dlje časa ni v uporabi.

msgid: Configure the duration in minutes for the screensaver.
Configure the duration in minutes for the sleeptimer. Select this entry and click OK or green to start/stop the sleeptimer
openpli: Določitev trajanja v minutah za časovnik spanja. Izberite ta vnos in pritisnite tipko \"OK\" ali zeleno tipko za vklop ali izklop časovnika spanja.

msgid: Configure the duration when the receiver should go to shut down in case the receiver is in standby mode.
openpli: Določitev trenutka, ko gre sprejemnik v stanje globokega spanja, če je sprejemnik v stanju pripravljenosti.

msgid: Configure the first audio language (highest priority).
Configure the first subtitle language (highest priority).
Configure the font size of the subtitles.
Configure the function of the '0' button when Picture in Picture is active.
openpli: Določitev funkcije tipke \"0\", ko je aktivna funkcija \"Slika v sliki\".

msgid: Configure the general audio delay of Dolby Digital sound tracks.
openpli: Določitev zamika zvoka pri Dolby Digital (AC3) zvočnih sledeh. Priporočena nastavitev je \"0\".

msgid: Configure the general audio delay of stereo sound tracks.
openpli: Določitev zamika zvoka pri stereo zvočnih sledeh. Priporočena nastavitev je \"0\".

msgid: Configure the hard disk drive to go to standby after the specified idle time.
openpli: Določitev časa po katerem naj bi trdi disk prešel v stanje pripravljenosti.

msgid: Configure the horizontal alignment of the subtitles.
Configure the initial fast forward speed. When you press the fast forward button, winding will start at this speed.
openpli: Določitev začetne hitrosti hitrega predvajanje. Ko pritisnete gumb za hitro predvajanja, se bo le-to pričelo z izbrano hitrostjo.

msgid: Configure the initial rewind speed. When you press the rewind button, winding will start at this speed.
openpli: Določitev začetne hitrosti predvajanja nazaj. Ko pritisnite tipko za previjanje, se bo le-to pričelo z izbrano hitrostjo.

msgid: Configure the latitude of your location.
openpli: Določitev zemljepisne širine glede na vaš trenutni položaj.

msgid: Configure the longitude of your location.
openpli: Določitev zamljepisne širine glede na vaš trenutni položaj.

msgid: Configure the minimum amount of disk space to be available for recordings. When the amount of space drops below this value, deleted items will be removed from the trash can.
openpli: Določitev najmanjšega prostora na shranjevalni napravi, ki je namenjena snemanju. Ko se velikost prostora približa določeni meji, pride do samodejnega izbrisa datotek, ki se nahajajo v smetnjaku.

msgid: Configure the number of days after which items are automaticaly removed from the trash can.
openpli: Določitev števila dni po katerem se datoteke samodejno izbrišejo iz smetnjaka.

msgid: Configure the number of days old timers are kept before they are automatically removed from the timer list.
openpli: Določitev števila dni ko so stari časovniki zadržani. Po tem obdobju se samodejno izbrišejo iz seznama.

msgid: Configure the offline decoding delay in milliseconds. The configured delay is observed at each control word parity change.
openpli: Določitev zamika offline dekodiranja v milisekundah. Ta nastavitev ni bistvena za delovanje vašega sprejemnika.

msgid: Configure the possible fast forward speeds.
openpli: Nastavitev možne hitrosti hitrega predvajanja naprej.
Določitev primarnega jezika za EPG sistem. Priporočena nastavitev je \"Prazno\".

msgid: Configure the refresh rate of the screen.
openpli: Določitev hitrosti osveževanja zaslona. Evropa uporablja sistem PAL, pravilna nastavitev je torej 50Hz.

msgid: Configure the screen resolution in PC output mode.
openpli: Določitev ločljivosti slike kadar se uporablja povezava z računalnikom.
Določitev druge zvočne sledi. Prva sled ima prednost pred drugo.
Določitev sekundarnega jezika za EPG sistem. Priporočena nastavitev je \"Prazno\".

msgid: Configure the sharpness of the video scaling.
openpli: Določitev ostrine slike. Osnovna nastavitev zadostuje za večino potreb.

msgid: Configure the skip time interval for the '1'/'3' buttons.
openpli: Določitev trajanja preskoka če se uporabi tipke \"1\" ali \"3\".

msgid: Configure the skip time interval for the '4'/'6' buttons.
openpli: Določitev trajanja preskoka če se uporabi tipke \"4\" ali \"6\".

msgid: Configure the skip time interval for the '7'/'9' buttons.
openpli: Določitev trajanja preskoka če se uporabi tipke \"7\" ali \"9\".

msgid: Configure the source of the frontend data as shown on the infobars. 'Settings' is as stored on the settings. 'Tuner' is as reported by the tuner.
openpli: Določitev izvora podatkov o kanalih, ki se pojavljajo v informacijski vrstici. Priporočena nastavitev je \"Kanalnik\", saj gre v tem primeru za najbolj točne informacije.

msgid: Configure the speed of the background deletion process. Lower speed will consume less hard disk drive performance.
openpli: Določitev hitrosti funkcije \"Brisanje v ozadju\". Nižja hitrost omogoči večjo zmogljivost shranjevalne naprave (npr. trdi disk).

msgid: Configure the speed of the fan
Configure the subtitle delay when timing information is not available.
openpli: Določitev zamika podnapisov v primeru, da manjkajo potrebne informacije za točnost pojavljanja podnapisov.
Določitev tretje zvočne sledi. Prva in druga zvočna sled imata prednost pred tretjo.

msgid: Configure the transparency of the OSD.
openpli: Določitev prosojnosti menijev oz. uporabniškega vmesnika.

msgid: Configure the transparency of the black background of graphical DVB subtitles.
openpli: Določitev prosojnosti črne podlage pri DVB podnapisih.
Nastavitev načina, v katerem se naj nahaja kanalnik.

msgid: Configure the type of status indication icons shown in the movielist.
openpli: Doložitev tipa statusne ikone, ki se sicer prikazuje v seznamu (video) datotek.

msgid: Configure the vertical position of the subtitles, measured from the bottom of the screen.
openpli: Določitev navpičnega položaja podnapisov, merjeno od spodnjega dela zaslona.

msgid: Configure the video output mode (or resolution).
openpli: Nastavitev omogoča izbiro ločljivosti zaslona. Če imate Full HD televizijo izberite ločljivost 1080i, če pa imate HD Ready televizijo izberite ločljivost 720p.

msgid: Configure the way in which the receiver changes channels.
openpli: Določitev načina preklopa med posameznimi kanali. Priporočena nastavitev je \"Črni zaslon\".

msgid: Configure this tuner using simple or advanced options, or loop it through to another tuner, or copy a configuration from another tuner, or disable it.
Configure where completed timers show up in the timer list.
openpli: Določitev položaja končanih časovnikov v seznamu le-teh.

msgid: Configure whether (and for how long) a second infobar will be shown when OK is pressed twice. The second infobar contains additional information about the current channel.
openpli: Določitev prikaza razširjene informacijske vrstice pri drugem pritisku na tipko \"OK\". Prikazane informacije se razlikujejo od uporabljene preobleke. Nekatere preobleke razširjene info. vrstice ne podpirajo!

msgid: Configure whether multi channel PCM sound should be enabled.
Configure whether multi channel sound tracks should be downmixed to stereo.
openpli: Nastavitev omogoča pretvorbo večkanalnega zvoka v stereo zvok. Priporočena nastavitev je \"Da\", sicer se lahko zgodi, da pri nekaterih TV kanalih zvok ne bo deloval.

msgid:
If your TV has a brightness or contrast enhancement, disable it. If there is something called "dynamic", set it to standard. Adjust the backlight level to a value suiting your taste. Turn down contrast on your TV as much as possible.
Then turn the brightness setting as low as possible, but make sure that the two lowermost shades of gray stay distinguishable.
Do not care about the bright shades now. They will be set up in the next step.
If you are happy with the result, press OK.
openatv:
Onemogočite poudarjanje svetlosti in kontrasta v kolikor ima vaš TV to funkcionalnost. V kolikor vsebuje nastavitev "dinamično", jo spremenite na standardno. Nastavite osvetlitev ozadja po vaši želji. Zmanšajte kontrast TV sprejemnika na najnižjo možno raven.
Zmanšajte nastavitev svetlosti na najnižjo možno raven, tako da bodo najnižji odtenki sive ostali razločni.
V tem trenutku ne skrbite za svetle sence na zaslonu, ponastavili jih boste v naslednjih korakih.
Če ste zadovoljni z nastavitvami, pritisnite OK.

msgid: Select '1.0' for standard committed switches, '1.1' for uncommitted switches, and '1.2' for systems using a positioner.
Select 'A' or 'B' if your aerial system requires this, otherwise select 'none'. If you are unsure select 'none'.
Select 'FBC SCR' if this tuner will connect to a SCR (Unicable/JESS) device. For all other setups select 'FBC automatic'.
Select 'Yes' when you want to configure this tuner for ATSC
Select 'Yes' when you want to configure this tuner for DVB-C
Select 'Yes' when you want to configure this tuner for DVB-S
Select 'Yes' when you want to configure this tuner for DVB-T
Select 'band' if using a 'universal' LNB, otherwise consult your LNB spec sheet.
Select 'enabled' if this tuner has a signal cable connected, otherwise select 'nothing connected'.
Select 'polarisation' if using a 'universal' LNB, otherwise consult your LNB spec sheet.

Select 'provider' to scan from the predefined list of cable multiplexes. Select 'bands' to only scan certain parts of the spectrum. Select 'steps' to scan in steps of a particular frequency bandwidth.
Select 'yes' if this tuner is connected to the SCR device through another tuner, otherwise select 'no'.
Select 'yes' to choose what bands or step sizes will be scanned.
Select 'yes' to include %s multiplexes in your search.
Select 'yes' to include symbol rate %s in your search.
Select 'yes' to include the %s band in your search.
Select 'yes' to only send the DiSEqC command when changing from one satellite to another, or select 'no' for the DiSEqC command to be resent on every zap.
Select Fast DiSEqC if your aerial system supports this. If you are unsure select 'no'.

msgid:
The overscan wizard has been completed.

Note: you can always start the Overscan wizard later,  via

Menu->Installation->System->Audio/Video->Overscan wizard

The overscan wizard helps you to setup your TV in the correct way.

For the majority of TV's, the factory default is to have overscan enabled. This means you are always watching a "zoomed in" picture instead of real HD, and parts of the user inferface (skin) may be invisible.

The yellow area means a 5% border area of a full HD picture will be invisible.
The green area means a 10% border area of a full HD picture will be invisible.

In other words, if the yellow box touches all four sides of your screen, you have at least 5% overscan on all sides.

If you see the tips of all eight arrowheads, then your TV has overscan disabled.

Test Pattern by TigerDave - www.tigerdave.com/ht_menu.htm

This is a multitype tuner. Available options depend on the hardware.

This is the order in which DiSEqC commands are sent to the aerial system. The order must correspond exactly with the order the physical devices are arranged along the signal cable (starting from the receiver end).
This option allows to reduce the block-noise in the picture. Obviously this is at the cost of the picture's sharpness.
This option allows to set the level of dynamic contrast of the picture.
This option allows you can to set the auto volume level.
This option allows you enable smoothing filter to control the dithering process.
This option allows you enable the vertical scaler dejagging.
This option allows you to add the softcam setup in the extensions menu.
This option allows you to alphabetically sort setup menu entries.
This option allows you to boost the blue tones in the picture.
This option allows you to boost the green tones in the picture.
This option allows you to change the virtuell loadspeaker position.
This option allows you to configure the Colordepth for UHD
This option allows you to configure the Colorimetry for HDR.
This option allows you to configure the Colorspace from Auto to RGB
This option allows you to configure the HDR type.
This option allows you to disable or change the virtuell loadspeaker position.
This option allows you to enable 3D surround softlimiter.
This option allows you to enable 3D surround sound.
This option allows you to enable or disable the 10 bit color mode
This option allows you to enable or disable the 12 bit color mode
This option allows you to force the HDR10 modes for UHD
This option allows you to force the HLG modes for UHD

This option allows you to hide and sort menu entries. When selecting user you can change order and hide menu items via the blue button. With the user defined hidden the blue button is not shown in the menus
This option allows you to power off the display.
This option allows you to show all symbols on the display.
This option allows you to show menu and/or plugin number quick links.
This option allows you to show menu paths.
This option allows you to view the old and new settings side by side.
This option can be useful for long HDMI cables.
This option set the level of surpression of mosquito noise (Mosquito Noise is random aliasing as a result of strong compression). Obviously this goes at the cost of picture details.
This option sets  the picture contrast.
This option sets the picture brightness.
This option sets the picture flesh tones.
This option sets the picture hue.
This option sets the picture saturation.
This option sets the scaler sharpness, used when stretching picture from 4:3 to 16:9.
This option sets the surpression of false digital contours, that are the result of a limited number of discrete values.
This option sets up the picture sharpness, used when the picture is being upscaled.
This setting allows the tuner configuration to be a duplication of how another tuner is already configured.

openpli: Posodobitev ni bila uspešna. Sprejemnik nima delujoče internetne povezave!

msgid: Use EIT EPG information when it is available.
openpli: EIT EPG se uporablja v primerih, ko TV postaje oddajajo tudi spored. Primer so slovenski kanali v DVB-T.

msgid: Use FreeSat EPG information when it is available.
openpli: FreeSat EPG se uporablja v primerih, ko TV postaje oddajajo tudi spored. FreeSat sistem uporabljajo nekatere TV postaje iz Velike Britanije.

msgid: Use MHW EPG information when it is available.
openpli: MHW EPG se uporablja v primerih, ko TV postaje oddajajo tudi spored. MHW sistem uporabljajo nekateri TV ponudniki iz Nizozemske.

msgid: Use Netmed EPG information when it is available.
openpli: Netmed EPG se uporablja v primerih, ko TV postaje oddajajo tudi spored. Netmed sistem uporabljajo TV ponudniki iz Grčije.
Uporaba sistema USALS za izbrani satelit

msgid: Use ViaSat EPG information when it is available.
openpli: ViaSat EPG se uporablja v primerih, ko TV postaje oddajajo tudi spored. Že ime nam pove, da je ta nastavitev uporabna za TV kanale iz paketa VIASAT (Skandinavija).

msgid: Use Virgin EPG information when it is available.
openpli: Virgin EPG se uporablja v primerih, ko TV postaje oddajajo tudi spored. Virgin sistem uporablja ponudnik TV vsebin iz Velike Britanije.

msgid: Use individual settings for each directory
openpli: Uporabi posamezne nastavitve za vsako mapo

msgid: Use the network wizard to configure selected network adapter
openpli: Za nastavljanje izbranega omrežnega vmesnika, izberite omrežni čarovnik.

msgid: Use the network wizard to configure your network\n
openpli: Za nastavljanje vašega omrežja, uporabite omrežni čarovnik.\n

msgid: Use the up/down keys on your remote control to select an option. After that, press OK.
openatv: Za izbiranje uporabite tipke gor/dol na vašem upravljalniku. Nato pritisnite OK.
openhdf: Za izbiranje uporabite tipke gor/dol na vašem upravljalniku. Nato pritisnite OK.
openpli: Za izbiranje uporabite tipke gor/dol na vašem daljinskem upravljalniku. Nato pritisnite tipko OK.
openvix: Za izbiranje uporabite tipke gor/dol na vašem upravljalniku. Nato pritisnite OK.

msgid: Use the wizard to set up basic features
Usually when the subtitle language is the same as the audio language, the subtitles will not be used. Enable this option to allow these subtitles to be used.
openpli: Če je nastavljen jezik podnapisov enak zvočni sledi (primer je angleški zvok in angleški podnapisi), se podnapisi ne bodo prikazovali. Vklopite omenjeno možnost, če želite, da se podnapisi vseeno prikazujejo.

msgid:
Video input selection

Please press OK if you can see this page on your TV (or select a different input port).

The next input port will be automatically probed in 20 seconds.
openpli:
Izbira video vira

Če vidite to sliko na zaslonu vašega TVja, pritisnite tipko OK ali pa izberite drugi vir.

Naslednji video vir bo samodejno preverjen čez 10 sekund.

View list of available EPG extensions.

View list of available default settings
View list of available display and userinterface extensions.

View list of available networking extensions

msgid: Warning!\nThis is an option for advanced users.\nReally disable timer conflict detection?
Warning: no LNB; using factory defaults.
openpli: Opozorilo: ni LNBjev; uporaba privzetih nastavitev.

msgid:
Welcome to the cutlist editor.

Seek to the start of the stuff you want to cut away. Press OK, select 'start cut'.

Then seek to the end, press OK, select 'end cut'. That's it.
openpli:
Dobrodošli v urejevalniku.

Poiščite začetek dela, ki ga želite izrezati. Pritisnite OK, izberite 'Začni brisati'.

Nato poiščite konec in pritisnite OK, izberite 'Končaj brisanje'.

msgid:
Welcome.

If you want to connect your receiver to the Internet, this wizard will guide you through the basic network setup of your receiver.

Press OK to start configuring your network
openpli:
Dobrodošli.

Če želite sprejemnik povezati na internet, vas bo omenjeni čarovnik vodil skozi vse potrebne nastavitve, ki so potrebne za delovanje internetne povezave na vašem sprejemniku!

Za nadaljevanje pritisnite tipko OK.

msgid:
Welcome.

This start wizard will guide you through the basic setup of your receiver.
Press the OK button on your remote control to move to the next step.
openpli:
Dobrodošli.

Začetni čarovnik vas bo vodil skozi osnovne nastavitve vašega sprejemnika.
Za nadaljevanje pritisnite tipko OK.

msgid: What type of service scan do you want?

When enabled enigma2 will load unlinked userbouquets. This means that userbouquets that are available, but not included in the bouquets.tv or bouquets.radio files, will still be loaded. This allows you for example to keep your own user bouquet while installed settings are updated
When enabled the Picture in Picture window can be closed with 'exit' button.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se funkcija \"Slika v sliki\" izklopi s pritiskom na tipko \"izhod\".

msgid: When enabled the arrow buttons around the OK button will follow the 'neutrino' style zap controls instead of the enigma2 style.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, smerne tipke okrog tipke OK pričnejo delovati v načinu neutrino, namesto v standardnem načinu enigma2.

msgid: When enabled the left, right, CH+/-, B+/-, P+/- buttons will follow the 'neutrino' style zap controls instead of the enigma2 style.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, tipke CH+/-, B+/-, P+/- pričnejo delovati v načinu neutrino, namesto v standardnem načinu enigma2.

msgid: When enabled the set top box is able to wakeup on LAN
openpli: Če ne nastavitev vključena, potem se lahko sprejemnik zbudi s pomočjo mrežne naprave (WOL).

msgid: When enabled the timer from the fallback tuner is imported

When enabled then when you select a new channel in the channel selection the channel selection will not close. It will only close when you select the current playing service. This is a kind of preview mode
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se ob izbiri novega kanala, seznam kanalov ne zapre. Zapre se le, če izberete kanal, ki se že predvaja.

msgid: When enabled you can control the volume with the arrow buttons instead of getting the channel selection list
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem lahko nastavljajte glasnost s smernimi tipkami.

msgid: When enabled you can customize the OpenWebIf settings for the fallback tuner
When enabled you can specify a timeframe to ignore the shutdown timer when the receiver is in standby mode
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se lahko določi časovno obdobje, znotraj katerega se časovnik za izklop ne upošteva - sprejemnik mora biti v stanju pripravljenosti

msgid: When enabled you can zap channels with the  CH+/-, B+/-, P+/- buttons instead of opening the channel selection list.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem lahko preklapljate kanale s tipkami CH+/-, B+/- in P+/- in to brez predhodnega odpiranja seznama kanalov.

msgid: When enabled you get the channel selection list via the OK button, the infobar toggle is then transfered to exit button
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se do seznama kanalov dostopa s pritiskom tipke OK, priklic informacijske vrstice pa se izvaja s tipko \"izhod\".

msgid: When enabled, AIT data will be included in http streams. This allows a client receiver to use HbbTV.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem so AIT podatki vključeni v HTTP tokove. Če uporabljate storitev HBBTV, potem je ta nastavitev bistvenega pomena!

msgid: When enabled, ECM data will be included in http streams. This allows a client receiver to do the descrambling.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem so ECM paketki vključeni v HTTP tokove. To omogoča sprejemnikom, da dekodirajo prejete podatke.

msgid: When enabled, EIT data will be included in http streams. This allows a client receiver to show EPG.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem so EIT podatki vključeni v HTTP tokove. To omogoča, da se na sprejemniku prikazuje okrnjen spored - samo za trenutni in naslednji dogodek.

msgid: When enabled, a popup message will be shown when a movie has finished and the next one will start.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, se ob prehodu iz enega filma na drugi film prikaže posebno obvestilo.

msgid: When enabled, a popup message will be shown when a recording starts.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, se pred začetkom snemanja prikaže posebno obvestilo.

msgid: When enabled, a radio background image will be visible while listening to a radio channel.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, se pri poslušanju radia prikazuje ozadje.

msgid: When enabled, a recording is allowed to interrupt live tv, when there are no free tuners.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem ima snemanje dovoljenje za prekinitev žive TV slike, vendar samo v primeru, ko ni prostega kanalnika.

msgid: When enabled, a warning will be displayed and the user will get an option to stop or to continue the timeshift.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se prikaže opozorilo in uporabnik ima možnost, da časovni zamik ustavi ali nadaljuje.

msgid: When enabled, always descramble receiving http streams. This takes up more resources (descrambling demuxers), only enable if necessary. Individual streams are always descrambled if 0x100 is added to the service type, regardless of this setting. Default off.
When enabled, authentication is required to watch http streams.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem je za ogled HTTP pretočnih vsebin potrebno preverjanje pristnosti.

msgid: When enabled, channel numbering will start at '1' for each bouquet.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem so kanali vedno številčeni od številke 1 naprej, ne glede na to v katerem paketu kanalov se nahajate.

msgid: When enabled, content with an aspect ratio of 4:3 will be stretched to fit the screen.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se vsebina, ki ima 4:3 razmerje slike, vedno razširi čez celoten zaslon.

msgid: When enabled, continue to the next bouquet when the last channel of the current bouquet is reached while changing channels.
openpli: Ko pridete do konca seznama kanalov, sprejemnik samodejno preide na naslednji paket kanalov.

msgid: When enabled, deleted recordings are moved to the trash can, instead of being deleted immediately.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem so izbrisani posnetki, namesto da bi bili takoj izbrisani, premaknjeni v smetnjak.

msgid: When enabled, display the EIT now/next eventdata in infobar. When disabled, display now/next eventdata from the EPG cache instead.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se v informacijski vrstici prikazujejo EIT podatki - gre za okrnjen spored, ki je na voljo samo za trenutni in naslednji dogodek.

msgid: When enabled, encryption info will be shown in the infobar (when supported by the skin).
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se v informacijski vrstici prikazujejo informacije o uporabljeni enkripciji kanala (odvisno od podpore preobleke).

msgid: When enabled, error messages related to zapping will not be shown.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se napake, ki so povezane s preklapljanjem kanalov, na zaslonu ne prikazujejo.

msgid: When enabled, external subtitles will be always turned on for playback movie.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se zunanji podnapisi ob pričetku predvajanja samodejno zaženejo.

msgid: When enabled, graphical DVB subtitles are preferred over teletext subtitles, when both types are available.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem imajo DVB podnapisi prednost pred teletekst podnapisi, ampak samo v primeru, da sta istočasno na voljo obe vrsti podnapisov.

msgid: When enabled, graphical DVB subtitles will be centered horizontally.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem so DVB podnapisi prečno osredinjeni.

msgid: When enabled, graphical DVB subtitles will be displayed at their original position.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se DVB podnapisi prikazujejo na njihovem izvirnem položaju.

msgid: When enabled, graphical DVB subtitles will be displayed in yellow, instead of the original color.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se DVB podnapisi prikazujejo v rumeni barvi.

msgid: When enabled, http streams are descrambled on the server side. The (remote) client receiver does not have to do descrambling. Default on.
When enabled, it is possible to leave the movieplayer with exit.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se lahko seznam posnetkov zapusti s pritiskom na tipko \"izhod\":

msgid: When enabled, measure power consumption to detect when the rotor stops turning (when supported by the tuner).
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se meri porabo električne energije, da bi se zaznal trenutek, ko rotor preneha s premikanjem. Omenjena funkcija deluje le če jo podpira kanalnik sprejemnika.

msgid: When enabled, reformat subtitles to match the width of the screen.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, se podnapisi prilagodijo širini zaslona.

msgid: When enabled, services may be grouped in multiple bouquets.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se s pritiskom na modri gumb, v seznamu kanalov prikažejo v pakete združeni kanali.

msgid: When enabled, show channel numbers in the channel selection screen.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem so poleg imen kanalov, v seznamu kanalov vidne tudi številke kanalov.

msgid: When enabled, subtitles for the hearing impaired can be used.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se lahko prikazujejo tudi podnapisi za gluhe in naglušne.

msgid: When enabled, subtitles for the hearing impaired will be preferred over normal subtitles, when both types are available.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem imajo podnapisi za gluhe in naglušne prednost pred normalnimi podnapisi. To velja samo v primeru, če sta istočasno na voljo obe vrsti podnapisov.

msgid: When enabled, teletext pages will be cached, allowing faster access.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem teletekst uporablja predpolnjenje, kar omogoči hitrejše delovanje.

msgid: When enabled, teletext subtitles will be displayed at their original position.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se teletekst podnapisi prikazujejo na njihovih izvirnih položajih.

msgid: When enabled, the VCR scart option will be shown on the main menu
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se v glavnem meniju pojavi možnost izbire menija \"VCR SCART\".

msgid: When enabled, the channel selection list will be hidden while listening to a radio channel
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem je pri poslušanju radijskih kanalov seznam kanalov skrit.

msgid: When enabled, the infobar will be displayed when a new event starts.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se informacijska vrstica prikaže vedno, ko pride do spremembe dogodka.

msgid: When enabled, the infobar will be displayed when changing channels.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se informacijska vrstica prikaže vedno, ko pride do preklopa na drug kanal.

msgid: When enabled, the infobar will be displayed when skipping forwards/backwards during media playback.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se informacijska vrstica pokaže vedno, ko med gledanjem multimedijskih datotek preskakujete nazaj ali naprej.

msgid: When enabled, the lenght of each recording will be shown in the movielist (this might cause some additional loading time).
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem je dolžina vsakega posnetka prikazana v seznamu datotek oz. posnetkov. Posledica tega je lahko daljši nalagalni čas.

msgid: When enabled, the receiver will automatically use the audio track which you selected before.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem sprejemnik samodejno uporabi zvočno sled, ki je bila pred tem že izbrana.

msgid: When enabled, the receiver will automatically use the subtitles which you selected before.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem sprejemnik samodejno uporabi jezik podnapisov, ki je bil pred tem že izbran.

msgid: When enabled, the receiver will no longer monitor the tuned transponder for possible changes. Do not use this option unless you know what you are doing.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem sprejemnik ne spremlja morebitnih sprememb trenutno uporabljenega transponderja oz. frekvence. Te nastavitve ne spreminjajte!

msgid: When enabled, the receiver will select an AC3 track (when available).
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem sprejemnik samodejno izbere AC3 zvok - če je le-ta na voljo.

msgid: When enabled, the receiver will select an AC3+ track (when available).
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem sprejemnik samodejno izbere AC3+ zvok - če je le-ta na voljo.

msgid: When enabled, this setting has more weight than 'Preferred tuner for recordings'.
When enabled, this setting has more weight than 'Preferred tuner'.
When enabled, timeshift starts automatically in background after specified time.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se časovni zamik v ozadju samodejno vključi po določenem času.

msgid: When enabled, use DHCP for the IP configuration.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem sprejemnik pridobi IP naslov samodejno - DHCP.

msgid: When enabled, your receiver will detect activity on the VCR SCART input.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem sprejemnik samodejno zazna aktivnost na vhodu SCART.

msgid: When nonzero, a recording will start earlier than the starting time indicated by the EPG.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se snemanje začne prej, kot je to določeno s sporedom. Če se po sporedu oddaja prične ob 10:00, lahko sprejemnik (odvisno od nastavitve) prične snemati že ob 09:50.

msgid: When nonzero, a recording will stop later than the ending time indicated by the EPG.
openpli: Če je nastavitev vključena, potem se snemanje konča kasneje, kot je to določeno s sporedom. Če se po sporedu oddaja konča ob 10:00, lahko sprejemnik (odvisno od nastavitve) konča s snemanjem ob 10:10.

msgid: When selected this allows video modes to be selected even if they are not reported as supported.
When the content has an aspect ratio of 16:9, choose whether to scale/stretch the picture.
openpli: Če ima vsebina razmerje slike 16:9, potem lahko določite, kako naj se slika prilagaja zaslonu. Priporočena nastavitev je \"Samodejno\".

msgid: When the content has an aspect ratio of 4:3, choose whether to scale/stretch the picture.
openpli: Če ima gledana vsebina razmerje slike 4:3, potem lahko določite, kako naj se slika prilagaja zaslonu. Priporočena nastavitev je \"Samodejno\".

msgid: Where to save temporary timeshift recordings?
openatv: Kam naj shranjujem začasne posnetke časovnega zamika?
openhdf: Kam naj shranjujem začasne posnetke časovnega zamika?
openpli: Kam naj shranjujem začasne posnetke časovnega zamika?
openvix: Kam naj shranjujem začasne posnetke časovnega zamika?

msgid: With T2MI RAW mode disabled (default) we can use single T2MI PLP de-encapsulation. With T2MI RAW mode enabled we can use astra-sm to analyze T2MI
With this option you can switch on the display in Deep Standby Mode.
With this option you can switch on the display in Standby Mode.
With this option you can switch the LED color or deactivate the LED.

openhdf: Napaka med snemanjem. Je disk poln?\n
openpli: Napaka med snemanjem. Je disk poln?\n
openvix: Napaka med snemanjem. Je disk poln?\n

msgid: Yes and save in movie dir
openpli: Da in shrani v mapo posnetkov

msgid: Yes, delete this movie and return to movie list
openpli: Da, izbriši datoteko in se vrni nazaj na seznam datotek

msgid: You PIN code is 0000. This is the default PIN code and it disables parental control!\n
You already have a channel list installed,\nwould you like to remove\n\"%s\"?
openatv: Seznam kanalov je že nameščen!\nBi ga radi odstranili\n\"%s\"?
openhdf: Seznam kanalov je že nameščen!\nBi ga radi odstranili\n\"%s\"?
openpli: Seznam kanalov je že nameščen!\nBi ga radi odstranili\n\"%s\"?
openvix: Seznam kanalov je že nameščen!\nBi ga radi odstranili\n\"%s\"?

msgid: You can continue watching TV etc. while this is running.
openatv: Med izvajanjem trenutne naloge, lahko nadaljujete z gledanjem trenutnega dogodka.
openhdf: Med izvajanjem trenutne naloge, lahko nadaljujete z gledanjem trenutnega dogodka.
openpli: Med izvajanjem trenutne naloge, lahko nadaljujete z gledanjem trenutnega dogodka.

msgid: You can enable if will be displayed extended EPG description for item.
You can only burn receiver recordings!
You can set how will be finished movieplayer with 'Exit' button.
You can set selected directory as 'root' directory for movie player.

You did not see all eight arrow heads. This means your TV has overscan enabled and presents you with a zoomed-in picture, causing you to loose part of a full HD screen. In addition this you may also miss parts of the user interface, for example volume bars and more.

Unfortunately, your model of receiver is not capable to adjust the dimensions of the user interface. If not everything is visible, you should change the installed skin to one that supports the overscan area of your TV.

When you select a different skin, the user interface of your receiver will restart.

Note: you can always start the Overscan wizard later,  via

menu->installation->system->Overscan wizard

You did not see all eight arrow heads. This means your TV has overscan enabled and presents you with a zoomed-in picture, causing you to loose part of a full HD screen. In addition to this you may also miss parts of the user interface, for example volume bars and more.

You can now try to resize and change the position of the user interface until you see the eight arrow heads.

When done press OK.
You didn't select a channel to record from.
openpli: Niste izbrali ustreznega kanala za snemanje.

Select 'Yes' to remove all keymap data. Selecting this option will remove all keymap override data and restore the default keymap definitions.

Select 'Yes' to remove all main settings configuration data. Selecting this option will set all Enigma2 settings back to their default values.  This will also cause Enigma2 to run the Welcome Wizard on restart.

Select 'Yes' to remove all media player resume data. Selecting this option will remove the data used to allow playback of media files to resume from the position where playback was last stopped. Playback position of recordings is not affected.

Select 'Yes' to remove all network data. Selecting this option will remove all network data including automounts and network connection data including connection accounts and passwords. This could cause some Enigma2 functions to fail if they are configured to use these network resources.
Select 'Yes' to remove all other files and directories not covered by the options above.

Select 'Yes' to remove all plugin configuration data. Selecting this option will remove all plugin configuration data that is stored in the Enigma2 configuration folder. This will cause all affected plugins to return to their default settings. This could cause some plugins to not function until configured.

Select 'Yes' to remove all settings, tuning data, timers, resume pointers etc. Selecting this option will restore the configuration to the initial settings before any configuration settings were applied. This is the most reliable form of Factory Reset.
Select 'Yes' to remove all timer configuration data. Selecting this option will clear all timers, autotimers and power timers.
Select 'Yes' to remove all tuning data. Selecting this option will remove all tuning and bouquet data and will make timers non functional until the receiver is retuned.

Select 'Yes' to remove all user customisations of skin data. Selecting this option will remove all user based skin customisations. All affected skins will return to their standard settings. This will also clear any customied boot logos and backdrops.
